{"tid":946524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞狗真係仆街黎！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T15:46:29.000Z","uid":177413,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82b46a73347333ebe6eb57460546320637463354","tid":946524,"uid":177413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"話說啱先收工<br />\n落到鋪頭樓下聽到有個阿婆大叫<br />\n：「偷野呀！偷野呀！」<br />\n跟住望去前面見到有個男人<br />\n抱住一大袋野急步行<br />\n隔左幾秒見到呀婆離遠追緊過黎<br />\n條街啲途人一路得個望字<br />\n我本身都諗住多一事不如少一事<br />\n猶疑左幾秒都係追啦<br />\n有個啊叔都一齊追<br />\n追到埋個男人側邊<br />\n嘩 屌你！高我成個頭，面露兇光<br />\n佢望一望我就掉低左袋野走左去<br />\n我都唔敢繼續追<br />\n阿叔都係屌下佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下身型可能兩個成年男人都㩒佢唔住<br />\n加上我係瘦弱毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就咁睇住佢拍下籮柚走咗去<br />\n之後阿婆嚟到話要報警<br />\n我話人都走咗啦報警都冇用<br />\n有個阿姐仲搭嘴話嗰啲人差唔多樣好難認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我想講嘅係南亞真係仆街種黎，最叻偷野搶野強姦打劫，<br />\n香港人要團結對抗外敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw袋野重到仆街，個南亞拎住仲行得勁快，我拎住行左幾步都喘哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53190c12d43df2a3cbebb21469ad697ad6dcf6af","tid":946524,"uid":155498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"樓主幾高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc7a530948a8549add7b04de0180ce146c7fe8e","tid":946524,"uid":177413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53190c12d43df2a3cbebb21469ad697ad6dcf6af","tid":946524,"uid":155498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"樓主幾高?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"米七，矮過九成連登仔"},{"pid":"f853c6c77f0b75a063503ee140f3f9a3ed611b03","tid":946524,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"肯追都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519b2130cf370191f199e7b96bc13a240bc47604","tid":946524,"uid":177413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f853c6c77f0b75a063503ee140f3f9a3ed611b03","tid":946524,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"肯追都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢走左嗰下其實都幾唔甘心<br />\n但又驚佢打柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91cdd0e10a66b86c93fa88a60816cf7baba2ed5","tid":946524,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:56:06.000Z","msg":"阿爺廚房1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/945047\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/945047</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n蝻亞狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7448dabcfa6bde4e03b2a17c88c2cf1d468f4681","tid":946524,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"519b2130cf370191f199e7b96bc13a240bc47604","tid":946524,"uid":177413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f853c6c77f0b75a063503ee140f3f9a3ed611b03","tid":946524,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"肯追都算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢走左嗰下其實都幾唔甘心<br />\n但又驚佢打柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"個個都葉問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb180af02631e2589e037a362cf3a2a9c413cb39","tid":946524,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=